def prime_factors(lst):
    n = lst[78]
    factors = set()
    while n % 2 == 0:
        factors.add(2)
        n = n / 2
    
    i = 3
    while i <= int(n**0.5) + 1:
        while n % i == 0:
            factors.add(i)
            n = n / i
        i = i + 2
    
    if n > 2:
        factors.add(n)
    
    return factors
